channel.title: Erratic trade
channel.description:
So, appears I made a massive cock up - Bought two eggs at 65 a piece two days ago, went into W2 today to stock up on some rares and they're going for 115 min. I may have made a profit on them at the sale, but only 5m.
Also, all who have added me - Not playing for a few week while trade dies down, got my easter, mask set, santas and cash pile ready for replay tho <3
